Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.57,0:00:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.91,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.85,0:00:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩光線  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.92,0:00:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.86,0:00:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.73,0:00:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.67,0:00:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.31,0:00:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.91,0:00:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.52,0:01:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.99,0:01:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.69,0:01:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.47,0:01:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.15,0:01:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(燒烤盒裝少女)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.79,0:01:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了一個禮拜的任務\N真的好懷念自己的床鋪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.70,0:01:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.07,0:01:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花．法蘭波瓦茲\N前來迎接妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎接？\N還真是稀奇呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.68,0:01:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，我想早點看到妳的臉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.35,0:02:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.38,0:02:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有啦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.39,0:02:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓您久等了，請慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.22,0:02:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，要加砂糖嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛奶呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.56,0:02:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味道很香吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.86,0:02:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳願意死嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.50,0:02:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳...妳剛才說了什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.47,0:02:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...\N對不起，因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請...請靜下來聽我說\N這裡面有很深的原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，先聽妳說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.05,0:02:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人是洛帝．利福曼\N是我很想交往的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.59,0:02:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.79,0:02:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後猛烈追求的結果\N昨天終於取得約會的約定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我卻睡過頭了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.43,0:02:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我為什麼要死呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...我把沒去的理由...\N不小心就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不小心就說同事死掉了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為比起家人，說同事死掉\N比較不會露出破綻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.88,0:03:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不想讓洛帝先生討厭我\N我是認真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我懂了，我懂了\N我就捨命陪君子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.82,0:03:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼\N連天使隊的人也要瞞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為洛帝先生家\N和軍隊的關係很深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.43,0:03:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後又很巧的\N這個消息又傳回了天使隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，謠言真是好可怕呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.64,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，拜託妳了\N請閉上眼睛死掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是笨蛋嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.58,0:03:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要為了這個無聊理由\N而非死掉不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.72,0:03:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在馬上回去跟大家說實情\N然後解決這件事，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.16,0:03:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BLUNDER  BUSS  FRONTLOCK槍\N妳覺得如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，感覺如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何？沒什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.47,0:04:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近越來越多像您這樣死去\N讓自己的存在消失的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.98,0:04:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒打算弄成那樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道，我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.91,0:04:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個葬儀社的人\N他不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.15,0:04:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣說呢\N我們是專業人士耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.46,0:04:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會辦好儀式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.03,0:04:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會辦好儀式的\N會辦好的....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.31,0:04:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到佛特會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還無法相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.68,0:04:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算全人類都死光了\N我想佛特還是會活下來的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，香草人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.42,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了佛特在祈禱著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.26,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說那是"生命復活的儀式"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔，真是溫柔的香草啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洛帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道該怎麼安慰妳才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.67,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我沒去赴約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼\N現在不是說這種話的時候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.78,0:05:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽說了\N她是為了保護小孩而去世的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.89,0:05:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了救差點被車輾到的小孩\N不顧一切的衝出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.29,0:05:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說到最後都還緊抱著小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後，雖然身負重傷\N仍溫柔微笑地問著"沒事吧"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是佛特的最後遺言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,編得真爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.17,0:05:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此偉大地犧牲自己\N宛如聖女般的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.21,0:05:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特對我們也很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.91,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有時候也很溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很會照顧人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是痛失英才啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.82,0:06:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂...\N好像死掉也不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.16,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，也請讓我一起送這位\N完美的人去天國吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何時火葬呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火...火葬？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.07,0:06:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才好像聽到佛特的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.40,0:06:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...在內部簡單的儀式之後\N就進行火葬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊\N那我明天也一起參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有...有你在，我就安心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂...等一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.52,0:06:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那是什麼，什麼火葬啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.66,0:06:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自然而然就變成這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.83,0:06:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真要火葬的話\N那我不就真的要死掉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.36,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於這點，您請放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.56,0:06:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這棺材可以耐住千度的高溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以保證它沒有缺陷嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它還貼有\N宇宙葬儀協會的認定標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.61,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在萬一的情形下\N還有這個緊急按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:07:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此\N按這個按鈕之後就可以逃出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.42,0:07:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，它會釋出氰化氫瓦斯\N可以不痛苦地死去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要不要換你進來看看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.26,0:07:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是佛特喜歡吃的不甜蘋果派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.57,0:07:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在檢查棺木的耐久性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利福曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於軍隊道德低落的問題\N可否說幾句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊道德的低落？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.85,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們難道不知道\N天使隊發生的那件意外嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.38,0:07:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好寂寞\N果然只有一把老槍是划不來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爛槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.79,0:07:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要亂射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.46,0:07:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於火葬的事情，我已經用\N佛特家的傳統作藉口改為土葬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也很噁心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.11,0:08:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天的葬禮，變成由軍隊主辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.35,0:08:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了救小孩而犧牲生命的\N銀河天使隊員，佛特修特倫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家為之感動不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.95,0:08:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍司令官表示，將考慮頒發\N名譽勳章給修特倫少佐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.33,0:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說軍司令官耶\N怎麼搞到這麼誇張啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.90,0:08:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，好像是洛帝跟記者說的\N洛帝真是讓人傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.14,0:08:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我該怎麼辦才好啊？\N在社會上我已經完全死掉了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請交給我們處理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.21,0:08:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由偽裝葬禮套餐\N切換成完全自我消滅套餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全自我消滅套餐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.69,0:08:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葬禮之後，可以在無人行星上\N過著無聲無息的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:09:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市民給佛特的花\N還有這麼多佛特喜歡的槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.97,0:09:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍？\N不行，現在不是高興的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.94,0:09:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都為佛特的勇氣而感動\N還會寄來更多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還會更多？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.75,0:09:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特一定也會很高興吧\N現在她已經是宇宙的英雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的英雄...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...\N嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.93,0:09:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，都是我不好\N使得事情變成這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.43,0:09:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特姊姊，我把我的槍送給妳\N在天國要記得使用喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.24,0:09:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得到了這地步\N死了也無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是謊言\N但是大家竟然對我如此惋惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶而也來無人行星玩玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，我也要一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.62,0:09:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來都是我不好\N我不能讓妳一個人孤孤單單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別這樣，啊...危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...這下就能提昇軍隊的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？我們怎麼了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.12,0:10:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的復活了，不愧是香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼蘭花也在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是...葬禮呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？妳是說佛特的葬禮嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.74,0:10:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為軍隊的偉大人物突然去世\N所以就緊急被更換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.94,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優和薄荷\N被派去戒護安全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.28,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過心地善良的香草\N一直為了佛特持續進行復活儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這爛墓地又是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.63,0:11:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍隊一撤手，因為預算的關係\N而無法盛大舉行儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奠儀全部都被葬儀社的人拿走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.03,0:11:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的保險又屬於\N在死亡的時候不給付的契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.34,0:11:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,俗話常說人在死去的時候\N才會知道自己真正的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個就是佛特妳的價值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.85,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.49,0:11:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣的話\N我要給它活個一百年、一千年...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個菜單是\N「天使罐頭附加炮塔」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來的題目是\N今後的天使隊會變成如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一，加入新成員一口氣變成十個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,二，成立姊妹隊的丘比特隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三，成立新團體"七點電影"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:11:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答案是一嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.35,0:11:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,答錯了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確答案是四...咩咩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.73,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.47,0:12:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.84,0:12:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在新月下的吊床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.78,0:12:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.42,0:12:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.33,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它睡著吧  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.47,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.48,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向牡羊座的你發出信號\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.48,0:13:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.76,0:13:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,DARING  LOVING  YOU

